values: Ok so there is nothing like ending a long work week with a car accident. But then I remembered that my work week doesn't end and that I have to work the next day. Anyway Katie is coming to watch some movies with me at work today. My friend Barry is going to make it a long day with nothing to do. I love storms.

Well first things first I am in a fantastic mood. I'm beyond burned out from work but feeling good. I have been out the past five nights and each one is better than the last. Even if I only got three hours of sleep last night before work it was all worth it and would do it again. I wish there was more to say but all I do is work. So I guess that's it for now.
I would just like to say last night was just wonderful. I really needed that and hope to do it again real soon. Thank you for making me smile.

I cant do this work thing anymore. I'm so out of it. I have to work all day tomorrow and hope I'm not boring when I take Katie out. I also need to go to the doctors when I get a day off. My mind is all over the place and can even slow it down enough to think right. Well I can't wait to go out tomorrow and will be the high point of my month.

I really don't know what I want to do anymore. i was starting to feel better but  now I'm scared of being hated. I wasn't going for that. Not talking wasn't to hurt anyone. I didn't think anyone would care if I stayed back for a wile. So now I'm more fucked than I was before.
Its not easy for me and im not happy.
Johnny Quest thinks your a sellout
I'm done with LiveJournal for  wile. Ill just hold it all in sorry everybody I feel this way.

I would just like to say right now that I am sick of the world treating me like shit. I have done nothing to deserve anything of this. I fucking try so hard to make things right and see them through. People fucking build me up and make me feel great and secure and just to stab me in the back and leave my to bleed out by myself. I'm always getting fucked and people say they understand and yet it doesn't stop them from bailing on me when something "better" or I should say easier comes along. I'm just not good for anyone. I guess I am  the guy you should drop when your friends how have no fucking clue whats going on tells you to. The guy who wasn't thinking about moving back home for you and who wouldn't do anything for you. Well fuck you.. Your happy now in your strong relationship with that guy you love so much. So now I'm here working seven days a week seven to six thinking if I knew what I know now would I have still given you as much as I did.
I hate life I really do
I have nothing to say right now maybe later I can write something

Ok so I am now going to be working for  wile. My buddy Josh walked out and I had to come in and cover on my day off. And thats why im here today. He was an asshole and im glad hes gone but this sucks. I really dont know if Ill be able to come home and if I do it wont be as long as I wanted to come home for. So yeah my life is great as it always it.
Fuck fuck fucking josh. Im working the rest of my life and dont think i can go home. Fuck.

did a new video today hope people like it.


http://www.youtube.com/profile?user=SouthShoreSka
I really don't know what to think anymore. All I know is that this is the most painful think I had ever had to go though.
I hate being like this. I'm depressed and my body is falling apart. Its going to be a long weekend.
I hate the little things like seeing her everyday before we go to work and sitting on the bus together. Or coming home after work to find her there.
Storms coming. Its about to rain.

So I found out a lot today about how I was really thought of. I was a mistake. Someone who should have been dropped before all this. I have been call an asshole for how I feel and was told I wasn't willing to do anything for someone. I would have done anything for her and I mean anything. Shes not who I thought she was. Shes not the person I fell in love with. I now know it will never be the way I want it to be and at this point I don't want it to be anything. I gave so much and tried so hard for her. She doesn't believe me when I said I loved her. No one knows what happen and no one can have an opinion of her or this but me. I'm so hurt on what was said today. I loved the past few months and thought I did a lot to show how I feel. If I knew this was going to happen... I don't know what I think about it. So I'm still coming home and my sisters having a party for me on Friday the 13th and I will be going to my Less Than Jake show with Mike. I'm going to have a good time and not think once about what I wanted my trip home to be. Well back to work.
Im not doing good at all

Ok so I really want to be with someone who will stay with me and not leave when someone else comes along. Someone who wont make me feel great about myself just to go when things get hard. Someone not to quit on me. Not one thing in the past few years has worked for me and I'm the only one who is willing to work for it. No matter how impossible it seem I keep going. I wont quit. I just wish I could say the same for everything else.







P.S. I am so going to hate being at that show this summer. To know she saw my favorite bands one of witch reminds me of her in every song with her boyfriend a week before is going to suck.

You said I fucked up. And now your happy with him. I know I can do better if giving a chance. I would make it right. I would fix the wrong. I would hold you tight and never let go. You gave up too soon. Never got to make it right. Had no say in our future. What is it you want me to do?

Ok so i guess if there is one thing I can say its every time I said I loved someone they didn't believe me and left me soon after. If there two things I find very important its love and sex. I don't know what to do anymore. I'm on my knees crying in to my hands.

His eyes upon your face.

His hand upon your hand.

His lips caress your skin.

Its more than I can stand!


Why does my heart cry?
Feelings I can't fight
You're free to leave me
But just don't deceive me
And please
Believe me when I say
I love you!
I really think ill be coming home for good.
I cant do this anymore. He makes her happier and she seems not to even think about what we had or could have. It hurts sso much to read what I do yet I cant stop. Fuck!
I hate life I really do im not even a thought anymore.
Today I wish I could say I was doing better today but im not. All I can say is its not over.
So I just took Lindsey of my myspace and sent her a message Im sure I dont mean. Im so lost in all this.

Ok so now im back to work and not feeling at all better. In fact I feel worst. I watched Risky Buniess the other night and the train part got me thinking and I saw another night of not sleeping. I try so hard not to look yet I cant help myself knowing its going to hurt. But comments, away messages, profiles. I dont know what to do. Part of me says to tell her to fuck off and end it for good. but part of me feel it might already be there and as always im the last to know. I thought about that this weekend. Im always the last to know. Ill sit there and think all is well and then as like all the times before im killing myself over what I did and thinking of what had happen. I have no one to talk to and no one to understand. I have noway to win or get what I want. As always im by myself to deal with this myself.

So last night I needed to get out so I went to the beach. I sat on the sea wall for a long long time till I was to cold to sit anymore. Then I got in my car and just went aroung the city with my sad songs on. When I got home I just sat in my car and did the same. I so hate the weekends now. I think way too much and it hurts.

Im not in a good place at the moment. Im at the point where I cant sleep and when I do I have great dreams about her. All day my thoughts are on them and all the stuff I wanted to do that he now takes the place of. I had planes for coming home. A trip a show. But now she will be going with him to see Less Than Jake. I need not to tell you how mad I am at that. I was cheated on and had no say to save it at all. Her mind was made up. After three years of some of the most amazing time she can just drop me like that. I just cant do this. I want to be with her so so bad. I love her I really do. I didnt say it to her and now it to late. I fucked up. I just want this to work. I want to be able to do it right and do it for real with her. I just want to say I dont buy that if its meant to be shit. If I did I would still be trying to be a pilot. You need to work for what you want and not give up on it. In three months I think Ill be coming home and its going to be so hard. I just want to kiss her again and hold her tight and now ill never let go. I would do anything for this. Its unfair I can only sit her and do nothing. Just think about the girl I love and her new boyfriend. When I said I love you I got hurt and when I didnt I got hurt. I dont know what to do. Why do I always get left behind. I try so hard I do. I just want it to be like it used to be. I fell for her hard and now im paying for something I told her I was uncomfortable  with. I want to be with her I need her in my life and not like this. Reading her away seeing someone else with her love and attention. Soon pictures and stories. I cant do this. Im lost hurt sick with pain. I want to go home and have a true romance with her. Everything makes me think of her and I now feel as if im not even thought about.
So today I went for a job and as he was showing me around I started to feel like I was going to pass out. I dont think im getting the job not and I feel like a joke. Someone care for me.

Last night sucked a lot. But whatever i dont care anymore. Thats a lie but im lieing to myself. I go home next week after a weekend at Disney. Its going to suck. And my brother wanted me to take him to downtown Disney and I said I cant. Im such a tool and an idiot. Im going home and going to try to hae fun. Im sure I will have a great time. So far I have two great shows im going to. Im going in to Boston with to ice skate and I get to meet some of my moms family. I wanted to show someone Boston and how I was away from all the shit I was going through here. Maybe if that happen I wouldnt be where I am now. Im still not sleeping and I need to shave. This girlat my brothers drum band thing trys to talk to me all the time but I just say a few words and call someone. I feel bad. Ill see her tonight and say sorry to her. I havent been calling my family up in Boston that much and need to do that as well. When I get back from home its all going to be different. Ill be in school ill have a job, a car, money and be able to do what I want. maybe ill feel better by then too. I doubt it.
I cant think of it in any other way then its over so she could date someone else.

these white pills aren't kind

i missed the grinding concrete where we sat past 8 or 9
and slowly finished laughing in the glow of our headlights
i've given a lot of thought to the nights we use to have
the days have come and gone
our lives when but so fast
i faintly remember breathing on your bedroom floor
where i laid and told you but you sweared you loved me more

do you care if i don't know what to say

will i shake this off pretend its all okay
that there someone out there who feels just like me

Well its the 8th and I can seem to find any reason to be happy today.
Its all fucking over I have nothing.

I never thought it would come to this but it did. Im really hurt and I cant take whats going on anymore. My life is just getting more fuckes up then it was before. I cant get a break. Just when things look to be getting better it all goes to shit. And now I have no one to go to. Caitlin seems not to care at all about me anymore and wont talk to me. My family cant help because they are not to good as well. I dont know what im going to do. Caitlin is number one on my list of things to fix. I dont know how good thats going to work out. I do get to go home but I dont know whats going to happen after that. Im so lost and im all alone.
I dont know whats going on with anything anymore. I hope Caitlin doesnt dump me.
I miss my Caitlin. Shes so cute.
